### FocusHome manual HTTP checks (VS Code REST Client or similar)
@base = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Parse (fallback without API key)
POST {{base}}/api/ai/parse-task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Tomorrow at 3 PM I will study algorithms for 45 minutes.",
  "timezone": "Europe/Istanbul"
}

### Manual task
POST {{base}}/api/tasks/manual
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Demo task",
  "preset_duration": 45,
  "difficulty_level": "HARD",
  "description": "From manual_test.http"
}

### List tasks
GET {{base}}/api/tasks

### Inventory
GET {{base}}/api/inventory

### Calendar template URL
POST {{base}}/api/calendar/template-url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finans Çalışması",
  "startDateTime": "2026-05-14T10:00:00",
  "endDateTime": "2026-05-14T11:00:00",
  "description": "Odak seansı"
}

### Grid state
GET {{base}}/api/grid
